WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 31=

00:01:41.370 --> 00:01:42.320 line:80%
Father,

00:01:42.320 --> 00:01:43.210 line:80%
why have you come out?

00:01:43.210 --> 00:01:44.090 line:80%
Father.

00:01:44.090 --> 00:01:45.180 line:80%
Song Shijun,

00:01:46.060 --> 00:01:48.010 line:80%
I want you to pay with blood!

00:01:55.010 --> 00:01:56.820 line:80%
Song Shijun killed the witness.

00:01:56.820 --> 00:01:58.090 line:80%
Seize the murderer.

00:02:02.490 --> 00:02:03.700 line:80%
What should we do, Zhao?

00:02:03.700 --> 00:02:04.730 line:80%
Should we go find Master?

00:02:06.420 --> 00:02:07.420 line:80%
Calm down.

00:02:07.420 --> 00:02:08.530 line:80%
Everyone, calm down.

00:02:11.140 --> 00:02:12.810 line:80%
There's no time. Save him first.

00:02:22.530 --> 00:02:23.370 line:80%
Take him and go.

00:02:30.060 --> 00:02:31.490 line:80%
Yang Heying, you useless fool.

00:02:32.370 --> 00:02:34.180 line:80%
Last year, I beat you.

00:02:34.180 --> 00:02:35.370 line:80%
You still haven't improved.

00:02:35.370 --> 00:02:36.733 line:80%
Cai Zhao, you wretched girl.

00:02:36.744 --> 00:02:38.061 line:80%
You're a traitor like Song Shijun,

00:02:38.072 --> 00:02:39.316 line:80%
colluding with the demonic sect.

00:02:44.300 --> 00:02:45.140 line:80%
Go help Yuzhi.

00:02:45.780 --> 00:02:46.620 line:80%
Sure.

00:02:52.160 --> 00:02:52.873 line:80%
Xingjia,

00:02:52.884 --> 00:02:54.030 line:80%
did you bring the duck feed?

00:02:54.090 --> 00:02:54.930 line:80%
I did.

00:02:55.410 --> 00:02:56.250 line:80%
Chase them.

00:03:21.810 --> 00:03:22.650 line:80%
How is he?

00:03:23.140 --> 00:03:24.900 line:80%
Yuzhi was poisoned
with purple vine poison.

00:03:24.900 --> 00:03:26.650 line:80%
I heard Uncle Lei mention it.

00:03:26.650 --> 00:03:29.060 line:80%
This poison is unique
to the Blood Marsh Forest.

00:03:29.060 --> 00:03:30.260 line:80%
It seals the meridians.

00:03:30.270 --> 00:03:31.140 line:80%
Within two days,

00:03:31.140 --> 00:03:32.289 line:80%
the victim will die.

00:03:32.300 --> 00:03:33.140 line:80%
Is there an antidote?

00:03:33.499 --> 00:03:34.702 line:80%
Guangtian Sect should have it.

00:03:34.780 --> 00:03:35.810 line:80%
Let's go back.

00:03:35.810 --> 00:03:36.650 line:80%
We can't.

00:03:36.860 --> 00:03:37.930 line:80%
We'll only die faster.

00:03:38.490 --> 00:03:40.210 line:80%
This whole matter has been strange.

00:03:40.650 --> 00:03:42.530 line:80%
The people who refined corpse slaves

00:03:42.530 --> 00:03:44.090 line:80%
should have been killed by Mu Qingyan.

00:03:44.896 --> 00:03:46.009 line:80%
Lord Song would never harbor

00:03:46.020 --> 00:03:47.810 line:80%
ambitions to dominate the Six Sects.

00:03:48.530 --> 00:03:50.780 line:80%
If Yang Heying truly wanted justice,

00:03:50.780 --> 00:03:52.650 line:80%
why didn't he wait for Master?

00:03:52.650 --> 00:03:54.490 line:80%
Instead, he launched a sudden attack.

00:03:55.140 --> 00:03:56.780 line:80%
Clearly, it was to seize the chance.

00:03:56.780 --> 00:03:58.180 line:80%
What exactly does he want?

00:03:58.860 --> 00:04:00.370 line:80%
Lord Song's condition

00:04:00.370 --> 00:04:01.530 line:80%
shows he was being controlled.

00:04:02.810 --> 00:04:03.860 line:80%
Also, Uncle Song

00:04:04.340 --> 00:04:05.180 line:80%
looked fair,

00:04:05.580 --> 00:04:07.490 line:80%
but he kept siding with Yang Heying.

00:04:07.490 --> 00:04:08.903 line:80%
If we return to Guangtian Sect now,

00:04:09.210 --> 00:04:10.476 line:80%
it would be walking into a trap.

00:04:10.580 --> 00:04:11.460 line:80%
So, what should we do?

00:04:12.490 --> 00:04:13.780 line:80%
All things counter each other.

00:04:14.650 --> 00:04:15.850 line:80%
Just like the Shanci Mushrooms.

00:04:15.850 --> 00:04:17.736 line:80%
There may be an antidote
in Blood Marsh Forest.

00:04:19.940 --> 00:04:21.610 line:80%
But that place is full of monsters.

00:04:21.610 --> 00:04:22.650 line:80%
They even eat people.

00:04:24.090 --> 00:04:24.930 line:80%
Hurry.

00:04:26.900 --> 00:04:28.020 line:80%
They can't have gone far.

00:04:28.020 --> 00:04:28.860 line:80%
Search!

00:04:30.020 --> 00:04:31.140 line:80%
To save Yuzhi,

00:04:32.020 --> 00:04:33.530 line:80%
even a dragon's lair must be entered.

00:04:38.820 --> 00:04:40.380 line:80%
They went toward Blood Marsh Forest?

00:04:41.970 --> 00:04:43.030 line:80%
Send people to pursue them.

00:04:43.730 --> 00:04:44.940 line:80%
Was Song Shijun captured?

00:04:45.210 --> 00:04:46.263 line:80%
Pang Xiong fought fiercely

00:04:46.650 --> 00:04:47.910 line:80%
and broke through the blockade.

00:04:48.136 --> 00:04:50.185 line:80%
The disciples outside
tried to surround them again,

00:04:50.290 --> 00:04:51.130 line:80%
but unexpectedly,

00:04:51.380 --> 00:04:52.340 line:80%
Lord Cai, Lady Ning,

00:04:52.650 --> 00:04:54.460 line:80%
and Mr. Dai suddenly arrived

00:04:54.970 --> 00:04:56.340 line:80%
and rescued Lord Song.

00:04:57.380 --> 00:04:59.140 line:80%
Why did Cai Pingchun come?

00:04:59.140 --> 00:05:00.900 line:80%
Song Shijun has lost his mind.

00:05:01.780 --> 00:05:02.900 line:80%
He can't say anything now.

00:05:23.530 --> 00:05:24.370 line:80%
Xiaofeng,

00:05:25.580 --> 00:05:26.500 line:80%
how is he?

00:05:26.500 --> 00:05:28.610 line:80%
Someone injected inner power
into his meridians.

00:05:29.780 --> 00:05:30.820 line:80%
It resembles the Puppet Gu,

00:05:31.812 --> 00:05:33.142 line:80%
but it's formed from inner power.

00:05:33.153 --> 00:05:34.223 line:80%
It can't be expelled.

00:05:34.700 --> 00:05:35.730 line:80%
If this continues,

00:05:36.140 --> 00:05:38.140 line:80%
Song Shijun may become a living corpse.

00:05:38.900 --> 00:05:40.033 line:80%
Is there any way to cure it?

00:05:40.170 --> 00:05:41.486 line:80%
He must return to Luoying Valley

00:05:41.530 --> 00:05:42.890 line:80%
and slowly dissolve it with herbs.

00:05:43.700 --> 00:05:45.020 line:80%
But we haven't found Zhao.

00:05:47.290 --> 00:05:48.130 line:80%
Lord Cai.

00:05:49.460 --> 00:05:50.300 line:80%
Uncle.

00:05:52.970 --> 00:05:53.810 line:80%
Lord Cai.

00:05:54.090 --> 00:05:55.650 line:80%
Uncle Pang suffered serious injuries.

00:05:55.650 --> 00:05:56.850 line:80%
We've applied medicine to him.

00:05:56.850 --> 00:05:57.830 line:80%
He's no longer in danger.

00:05:58.290 --> 00:05:59.130 line:80%
Good.

00:06:00.050 --> 00:06:00.640 line:80%
By the way,

00:06:00.651 --> 00:06:01.904 line:80%
have you contacted your father?

00:06:02.970 --> 00:06:04.290 line:80%
Father has received the news.

00:06:04.290 --> 00:06:05.303 line:80%
He'll arrive in two days.

00:06:06.140 --> 00:06:06.980 line:80%
Darn it.

00:06:07.140 --> 00:06:09.140 line:80%
The Guangtian disciples
sent the wrong message.

00:06:09.386 --> 00:06:11.455 line:80%
It made us run to such a distant place
for nothing.

00:06:11.580 --> 00:06:12.420 line:80%
They

00:06:12.610 --> 00:06:14.110 line:80%
must have deliberately lured us away.

00:06:14.580 --> 00:06:15.420 line:80%
They?

00:06:20.460 --> 00:06:21.300 line:80%
Uncle.

00:06:22.580 --> 00:06:23.420 line:80%
Uncle.

00:06:36.540 --> 00:06:37.610 line:80%
His meridians are in chaos.

00:06:37.610 --> 00:06:38.820 line:80%
He must return to the valley.

00:06:39.090 --> 00:06:40.530 line:80%
With Zhao's cultivation,

00:06:40.530 --> 00:06:42.043 line:80%
she should be able to protect herself.

00:06:42.550 --> 00:06:43.410 line:80%
Besides,

00:06:43.410 --> 00:06:44.503 line:80%
Qi will arrive soon as well.

00:06:45.170 --> 00:06:46.010 line:80%
Listen.

00:06:46.290 --> 00:06:47.203 line:80%
Saving lives is urgent.

00:06:47.290 --> 00:06:48.343 line:80%
We can only do it this way.

00:06:49.380 --> 00:06:53.940 line:80%
(Blood Marsh Forest)

00:06:57.090 --> 00:06:58.460 line:80%
Ahead is Blood Marsh Forest.

00:07:09.380 --> 00:07:10.720 line:80%
The Curved Formation of Siqi Sect.

00:07:45.700 --> 00:07:46.820 line:80%
There's a maze formation.

00:07:48.140 --> 00:07:48.980 line:80%
You can't get in.

00:07:49.290 --> 00:07:50.140 line:80%
How do you know?

00:07:50.140 --> 00:07:51.820 line:80%
We tried several times

00:07:51.820 --> 00:07:52.730 line:80%
and almost died inside.

00:07:52.730 --> 00:07:53.730 line:80%
Talkative.

00:07:59.210 --> 00:08:00.050 line:80%
Let's go.

00:08:03.920 --> 00:08:04.780 line:80%
Zhao,

00:08:04.780 --> 00:08:06.170 line:80%
they are also going to the forest.

00:08:06.170 --> 00:08:07.410 line:80%
Since it's dangerous,

00:08:07.410 --> 00:08:09.156 line:80%
it's better to have more people
than fewer.

00:08:10.170 --> 00:08:11.820 line:80%
Yuzhi can't wait any longer.

00:08:11.820 --> 00:08:13.340 line:80%
If we want to save his life,

00:08:13.340 --> 00:08:14.850 line:80%
we have to follow them in.

00:08:17.410 --> 00:08:18.410 line:80%
Zhao.

00:08:22.850 --> 00:08:24.070 line:80%
In urgent times, we must adapt.

00:08:24.700 --> 00:08:25.853 line:80%
This is the only way for now.

00:08:44.450 --> 00:08:45.290 line:80%
Young Master,

00:08:45.690 --> 00:08:46.530 line:80%
before it gets dark,

00:08:46.980 --> 00:08:48.020 line:80%
should we go further in?

00:08:48.500 --> 00:08:49.340 line:80%
I'm tired.

00:08:49.930 --> 00:08:51.330 line:80%
Let's rest here for today.

00:08:55.690 --> 00:08:56.530 line:80%
Young Master,

00:08:56.740 --> 00:08:58.900 line:80%
Miss Cai is behind us.

00:09:03.380 --> 00:09:04.220 line:80%
Zhao,

00:09:04.380 --> 00:09:05.900 line:80%
should we rest here for the night

00:09:05.900 --> 00:09:06.780 line:80%
and set out at dawn?

00:09:07.050 --> 00:09:08.570 line:80%
I'm afraid Yuzhi won't wait.

00:09:09.570 --> 00:09:11.100 line:80%
It's almost dark.

00:09:11.100 --> 00:09:13.020 line:80%
The forest is dangerous by day.

00:09:13.020 --> 00:09:13.860 line:80%
Going at night

00:09:14.650 --> 00:09:16.170 line:80%
would be a death sentence.

00:09:25.780 --> 00:09:26.760 line:80%
Let's wait until morning.

00:09:28.220 --> 00:09:29.060 line:80%
Young Master,

00:09:29.380 --> 00:09:30.450 line:80%
I'll gather some firewood

00:09:30.450 --> 00:09:31.290 line:80%
and make a fire.

00:09:36.530 --> 00:09:37.370 line:80%
I'll find

00:09:38.020 --> 00:09:38.860 line:80%
some food.

00:09:57.220 --> 00:09:59.410 line:80%
The poison spreads too fast on the way.

00:09:59.410 --> 00:10:01.220 line:80%
We need some medicine to suppress it.

00:10:01.220 --> 00:10:03.150 line:80%
But all my medicine fell
at Guangtian Sect.

00:10:03.150 --> 00:10:04.050 line:80%
Zhao,

00:10:04.050 --> 00:10:04.890 line:80%
what should we do?

00:10:23.780 --> 00:10:24.650 line:80%
Master You,

00:10:25.530 --> 00:10:27.900 line:80%
did you bring some antidotes?

00:10:35.530 --> 00:10:37.570 line:80%
We are people of the demonic sect.

00:10:37.570 --> 00:10:38.550 line:80%
Even if we have medicine,

00:10:38.810 --> 00:10:39.930 line:80%
we dare not give it to you.

00:10:40.620 --> 00:10:42.290 line:80%
If you were whipped again,

00:10:42.690 --> 00:10:44.020 line:80%
we couldn't bear it.

00:10:44.500 --> 00:10:45.410 line:80%
Does that make sense?

00:10:45.980 --> 00:10:46.820 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:10:47.330 --> 00:10:49.740 line:80%
I know some methods to drive out poison.

00:10:51.220 --> 00:10:52.100 line:80%
But...

00:10:52.100 --> 00:10:52.940 line:80%
Talkative.

00:10:55.100 --> 00:10:56.050 line:80%
Go if you want.

00:10:58.140 --> 00:10:59.500 line:80%
Miss Cai, take this,

00:10:59.500 --> 00:11:00.340 line:80%
and help me roast it.

00:11:28.450 --> 00:11:29.856 line:80%
The corpse slaves at Guangtian Sect

00:11:30.290 --> 00:11:31.130 line:80%
were not made by me.

00:11:32.170 --> 00:11:33.010 line:80%
I know.

00:11:53.650 --> 00:11:54.490 line:80%
Apply it externally.

00:12:37.740 --> 00:12:39.330 line:80%
It should be fine by tomorrow night.

00:12:41.380 --> 00:12:43.450 line:80%
The Six Sects appreciate it.

00:12:43.450 --> 00:12:44.780 line:80%
I'll remember this favor.

00:12:44.780 --> 00:12:46.330 line:80%
Mr. Song has done us a kindness.

00:12:46.330 --> 00:12:47.530 line:80%
This is something we owe him.

00:12:57.450 --> 00:12:58.290 line:80%
Zhao,

00:12:58.690 --> 00:12:59.690 line:80%
look at this wound.

00:13:00.220 --> 00:13:01.410 line:80%
From the wound,

00:13:01.930 --> 00:13:03.620 line:80%
the attacker's skill is not very great,

00:13:04.450 --> 00:13:06.900 line:80%
but they are very familiar with Yuzhi.

00:13:07.690 --> 00:13:09.710 line:80%
They must have observed from the side,

00:13:09.710 --> 00:13:10.620 line:80%
predicted

00:13:10.620 --> 00:13:12.170 line:80%
Yuzhi's next move,

00:13:12.170 --> 00:13:13.780 line:80%
and fired a hidden weapon.

00:13:13.780 --> 00:13:16.050 line:80%
The only person capable of this

00:13:18.650 --> 00:13:19.620 line:80%
is...

00:13:25.380 --> 00:13:26.220 line:80%
Xingjia,

00:13:26.410 --> 00:13:27.690 line:80%
you must take care of Yuzhi.

00:13:28.170 --> 00:13:29.283 line:80%
I'll bring back the antidote

00:13:29.450 --> 00:13:30.620 line:80%
before sunset.

00:13:30.760 --> 00:13:31.620 line:80%
Okay.

00:13:31.620 --> 00:13:32.530 line:80%
Zhao,

00:13:32.530 --> 00:13:33.370 line:80%
be careful.

00:13:53.410 --> 00:13:55.290 line:80%
Too many people are of no use.

00:13:56.020 --> 00:13:56.860 line:80%
If I haven't returned

00:13:57.530 --> 00:13:58.450 line:80%
by sunset,

00:13:59.020 --> 00:14:00.100 line:80%
burn this forest.

00:14:00.860 --> 00:14:01.700 line:80%
Yes.

00:14:20.810 --> 00:14:22.450 line:80%
This is the Blood Marsh Forest.

00:14:33.220 --> 00:14:34.060 line:80%
Stop.

00:14:49.220 --> 00:14:50.530 line:80%
These vines have traps.

00:14:51.050 --> 00:14:51.900 line:80%
There is a maze here.

00:14:53.650 --> 00:14:55.100 line:80%
If the golden thread runs out

00:14:55.100 --> 00:14:56.290 line:80%
and we haven't gotten out,

00:14:56.753 --> 00:14:58.106 line:80%
we'll have to return the same way.

00:15:07.170 --> 00:15:08.010 line:80%
Follow me.

00:15:35.780 --> 00:15:37.106 line:80%
We are back at the starting point.

00:15:38.140 --> 00:15:39.786 line:80%
The last bundle of thread
is almost gone.

00:15:40.410 --> 00:15:41.250 line:80%
Let's go back.

00:15:54.780 --> 00:15:55.620 line:80%
Zhao!

00:16:36.220 --> 00:16:37.060 line:80%
Thank you.

00:16:37.780 --> 00:16:38.620 line:80%
Does it hurt?

00:16:41.330 --> 00:16:42.170 line:80%
Not really.

00:16:42.330 --> 00:16:43.170 line:80%
I forgot long ago.

00:16:56.580 --> 00:16:58.310 line:80%
♪In days gone by♪

00:16:58.620 --> 00:17:00.170 line:80%
♪Willows swayed gently♪

00:17:00.470 --> 00:17:03.220 line:80%
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

00:17:04.190 --> 00:17:05.380 line:80%
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

00:17:05.390 --> 00:17:06.860 line:80%
♪A fleeting glance♪

00:17:07.030 --> 00:17:07.940 line:80%
♪And then♪

00:17:07.950 --> 00:17:10.900 line:80%
♪Love consumed me♪

00:17:11.710 --> 00:17:13.260 line:80%
♪Now I think of you♪

00:17:14.180 --> 00:17:15.273 line:80%
It's more dangerous inside.

00:17:15.940 --> 00:17:16.780 line:80%
You go back first.

00:17:17.610 --> 00:17:18.450 line:80%
I'll go alone.

00:17:19.810 --> 00:17:20.650 line:80%
No.

00:17:21.670 --> 00:17:22.700 line:80%
♪Scattered petals♪

00:17:22.710 --> 00:17:24.580 line:80%
♪Cover the ground♪

00:17:24.610 --> 00:17:25.890 line:80%
For Song Yuzhi,

00:17:26.906 --> 00:17:28.146 line:80%
you'd risk yourself like this?

00:17:28.440 --> 00:17:33.120 line:80%
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

00:17:33.290 --> 00:17:34.130 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:17:35.090 --> 00:17:36.660 line:80%
I'll bring back the antidote.

00:17:38.020 --> 00:17:39.050 line:80%
Do you know the way?

00:17:40.780 --> 00:17:43.310 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:17:43.590 --> 00:17:47.840 line:80%
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

00:17:48.140 --> 00:17:50.720 line:80%
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

00:17:51.100 --> 00:17:54.160 line:80%
♪Tears are like pearls♪

00:17:54.180 --> 00:17:55.500 line:80%
When the fog cleared just now,

00:17:55.796 --> 00:17:57.290 line:80%
I realized the terrain is very similar

00:17:57.290 --> 00:17:58.660 line:80%
to Mu Donglie's underground palace.

00:17:59.330 --> 00:18:00.700 line:80%
It confirmed my guess.

00:18:00.866 --> 00:18:02.546 line:80%
It's also the formation
of Luoying Valley?

00:18:02.570 --> 00:18:04.130 line:80%
Yes and no.

00:18:04.500 --> 00:18:06.890 line:80%
To be precise,
it's our ancient formation.

00:18:06.890 --> 00:18:09.020 line:80%
It has been changed many times,

00:18:09.020 --> 00:18:10.420 line:80%
but I heard my aunt mention it.

00:18:10.940 --> 00:18:12.050 line:80%
Did Ms. Cai mention

00:18:12.050 --> 00:18:13.330 line:80%
a way to break the formation?

00:18:13.610 --> 00:18:14.460 line:80%
She didn't,

00:18:14.733 --> 00:18:15.719 line:80%
but I know the principles

00:18:15.980 --> 00:18:17.610 line:80%
of the formation's changes.

00:18:18.500 --> 00:18:19.780 line:80%
If I'm right,

00:18:19.780 --> 00:18:21.050 line:80%
we are now here.

00:18:21.460 --> 00:18:22.300 line:80%
Gen three,

00:18:22.810 --> 00:18:23.650 line:80%
Dui four,

00:18:24.130 --> 00:18:24.970 line:80%
Kan minus two.

00:18:29.290 --> 00:18:30.130 line:80%
Follow me.

00:18:45.980 --> 00:18:46.820 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:18:59.020 --> 00:19:00.050 line:80%
It's them.

00:19:00.780 --> 00:19:01.620 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:19:01.940 --> 00:19:03.050 line:80%
they mean no harm.

00:19:03.530 --> 00:19:04.460 line:80%
Where is Zhao?

00:19:05.370 --> 00:19:06.660 line:80%
Zhao went

00:19:07.570 --> 00:19:08.700 line:80%
to the forest with Mu Qingyan

00:19:08.700 --> 00:19:09.980 line:80%
to find the antidote for you.

00:19:11.890 --> 00:19:13.130 line:80%
Trying to trick Zhao again.

00:19:14.020 --> 00:19:14.860 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:19:21.050 --> 00:19:21.890 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:19:22.290 --> 00:19:23.780 line:80%
saving your life is the priority.

00:19:24.130 --> 00:19:25.370 line:80%
As for Mu Qingyan,

00:19:26.050 --> 00:19:27.530 line:80%
Zhao is clever enough

00:19:27.530 --> 00:19:28.660 line:80%
not to be fooled.

00:19:37.890 --> 00:19:38.850 line:80%
It shouldn't be.

00:19:40.020 --> 00:19:41.570 line:80%
Why is this a dead end?

00:19:41.570 --> 00:19:42.410 line:80%
The path is correct.

00:19:42.950 --> 00:19:45.090 line:80%
I observed the terrain from above
on the Golden Peng.

00:19:45.090 --> 00:19:46.890 line:80%
To find the blood purple vine,

00:19:46.890 --> 00:19:48.330 line:80%
we must pass through this forest.

00:19:55.420 --> 00:19:56.660 line:80%
The fog is poisonous.

00:19:57.740 --> 00:19:58.700 line:80%
Time is short.

00:19:59.500 --> 00:20:00.610 line:80%
I'll clear the way for you.

00:20:01.290 --> 00:20:02.180 line:80%
Mu Qingyan!

00:20:17.700 --> 00:20:18.540 line:80%
Mu Qingyan!

00:20:19.420 --> 00:20:20.260 line:80%
Mu Qingyan!

00:20:20.710 --> 00:20:21.570 line:80%
Are you alright?

00:20:21.570 --> 00:20:22.410 line:80%
Don't worry about me.

00:20:22.850 --> 00:20:24.170 line:80%
- Hurry inside.
- No.

00:20:30.370 --> 00:20:31.210 line:80%
Someone's coming.

00:20:38.660 --> 00:20:40.100 line:80%
(Granny Jiang)

00:20:41.740 --> 00:20:42.700 line:80%
Zhengyang?

00:20:46.090 --> 00:20:46.980 line:80%
Pingshu?

00:20:49.130 --> 00:20:50.500 line:80%
I've gone senile.

00:20:51.810 --> 00:20:53.850 line:80%
You two are their children, right?

00:20:53.850 --> 00:20:54.690 line:80%
Granny,

00:20:55.220 --> 00:20:56.130 line:80%
you've met them?

00:21:13.890 --> 00:21:14.730 line:80%
Come.

00:21:15.130 --> 00:21:16.420 line:80%
Thank you, Granny Jiang.

00:21:16.850 --> 00:21:19.610 line:80%
You're affected by the maze's poison.

00:21:20.220 --> 00:21:22.940 line:80%
Drink this licorice decoction
for two days;

00:21:22.940 --> 00:21:24.980 line:80%
the poison will naturally clear.

00:21:25.460 --> 00:21:26.810 line:80%
I've already sent someone

00:21:26.810 --> 00:21:28.740 line:80%
to fetch your friends.

00:21:29.090 --> 00:21:30.850 line:80%
They should arrive before nightfall.

00:21:31.220 --> 00:21:32.980 line:80%
His purple vine poison

00:21:32.980 --> 00:21:35.180 line:80%
can only be treated
with our Night Orchid.

00:21:35.570 --> 00:21:37.020 line:80%
You siblings

00:21:37.020 --> 00:21:40.290 line:80%
really take after your parents.

00:21:40.740 --> 00:21:41.580 line:80%
Granny Jiang,

00:21:42.370 --> 00:21:44.290 line:80%
we are not siblings.

00:21:44.890 --> 00:21:46.810 line:80%
The Pingshu you mentioned

00:21:47.330 --> 00:21:48.170 line:80%
is my aunt.

00:21:48.810 --> 00:21:51.530 line:80%
Master Zhengyang is his uncle.

00:21:52.130 --> 00:21:52.970 line:80%
Then,

00:21:53.810 --> 00:21:55.660 line:80%
did they eventually marry?

00:21:58.810 --> 00:21:59.700 line:80%
They did,

00:22:00.460 --> 00:22:01.850 line:80%
but they have both passed away.

00:22:04.020 --> 00:22:05.370 line:80%
What a pity.

00:22:05.810 --> 00:22:07.570 line:80%
They were so young.

00:22:08.740 --> 00:22:09.660 line:80%
Granny Jiang,

00:22:10.420 --> 00:22:11.260 line:80%
how did my aunt

00:22:11.660 --> 00:22:14.290 line:80%
and her uncle get in?

00:22:14.890 --> 00:22:17.890 line:80%
They suddenly broke in.

00:22:18.420 --> 00:22:19.890 line:80%
We were all shocked

00:22:20.370 --> 00:22:22.810 line:80%
and thought the maze had failed.

00:22:23.610 --> 00:22:27.180 line:80%
They said Master Zhengyang's friend
had also been poisoned

00:22:27.530 --> 00:22:29.420 line:80%
and needed the Night Orchid
for the remedy.

00:22:29.940 --> 00:22:31.570 line:80%
We naturally agreed.

00:22:32.610 --> 00:22:36.180 line:80%
After taking a few branches, they left.

00:22:36.740 --> 00:22:37.580 line:80%
Granny Jiang,

00:22:38.460 --> 00:22:40.090 line:80%
can we go see

00:22:40.370 --> 00:22:41.210 line:80%
the Night Orchid?

00:22:41.850 --> 00:22:46.660 line:80%
Yes, but don't get too close.

00:22:47.130 --> 00:22:47.980 line:80%
Why?

00:22:48.700 --> 00:22:50.370 line:80%
Pingshu said

00:22:51.220 --> 00:22:53.890 line:80%
this must not be shown to others.

00:22:54.610 --> 00:22:56.700 line:80%
Getting too close is dangerous.

00:22:58.050 --> 00:23:00.290 line:80%
Didn't she also come
for the Night Orchid?

00:23:00.780 --> 00:23:02.660 line:80%
Why would she say that?

00:23:02.660 --> 00:23:04.890 line:80%
She said this on her second visit.

00:23:05.530 --> 00:23:07.530 line:80%
After leaving with Master Zhengyang,

00:23:07.980 --> 00:23:09.370 line:80%
a year and a half later,

00:23:09.370 --> 00:23:10.740 line:80%
she returned and asked

00:23:11.220 --> 00:23:15.370 line:80%
if Master Zhengyang had come back too.

00:23:16.290 --> 00:23:17.420 line:80%
I said yes.

00:23:18.570 --> 00:23:20.980 line:80%
Shortly before her return,

00:23:20.980 --> 00:23:25.130 line:80%
Master Zhengyang had taken
a few more branches,

00:23:26.700 --> 00:23:29.850 line:80%
and Pingshu cried.

00:23:30.850 --> 00:23:32.890 line:80%
She cried so sorrowfully.

00:23:36.610 --> 00:23:38.090 line:80%
Why did my aunt cry?

00:23:38.780 --> 00:23:40.050 line:80%
She wouldn't say.

00:23:41.020 --> 00:23:44.020 line:80%
She just reminded us
to watch over the Night Orchid.

00:23:44.460 --> 00:23:46.700 line:80%
Before leaving, she set up a formation

00:23:47.220 --> 00:23:48.700 line:80%
to keep people away.

00:23:49.810 --> 00:23:51.020 line:80%
Why did Master Zhengyang

00:23:51.530 --> 00:23:53.290 line:80%
come twice

00:23:54.050 --> 00:23:55.420 line:80%
instead of taking more

00:23:56.420 --> 00:23:57.700 line:80%
at once?

00:23:58.890 --> 00:24:01.220 line:80%
The Night Orchid is very delicate.

00:24:02.020 --> 00:24:03.940 line:80%
Once removed from the forest,

00:24:03.940 --> 00:24:08.130 line:80%
it will wither like firewood
in six months,

00:24:08.130 --> 00:24:10.050 line:80%
losing all medicinal properties.

00:24:11.420 --> 00:24:13.370 line:80%
Our great benefactor

00:24:13.370 --> 00:24:15.610 line:80%
transplanted it more than 50 times

00:24:15.610 --> 00:24:17.370 line:80%
to save a few plants.

00:24:19.890 --> 00:24:20.890 line:80%
Your great benefactor?

00:24:21.980 --> 00:24:24.780 line:80%
That was Cai Anning.

00:24:24.780 --> 00:24:26.130 line:80%
Cai Anning?

00:24:26.890 --> 00:24:29.050 line:80%
She was our third demoness...

00:24:30.180 --> 00:24:31.020 line:80%
our heroine.

00:24:33.980 --> 00:24:35.370 line:80%
When I was a child,

00:24:36.700 --> 00:24:38.850 line:80%
my mother said

00:24:38.850 --> 00:24:40.700 line:80%
she was predicted at birth

00:24:40.700 --> 00:24:41.810 line:80%
not to live past three.

00:24:42.850 --> 00:24:44.220 line:80%
After surviving three,

00:24:44.780 --> 00:24:47.420 line:80%
it was said
she wouldn't reach adulthood.

00:24:48.530 --> 00:24:51.370 line:80%
So, she sought

00:24:52.220 --> 00:24:53.940 line:80%
all kinds of rare herbs

00:24:54.420 --> 00:24:57.330 line:80%
in the world,

00:24:58.090 --> 00:24:58.940 line:80%
even stealing seeds

00:24:58.940 --> 00:25:00.740 line:80%
from the Li sect.

00:25:00.740 --> 00:25:02.810 line:80%
She was later pursued by the sect.

00:25:03.330 --> 00:25:05.610 line:80%
Our great benefactor said

00:25:06.290 --> 00:25:10.090 line:80%
she was chased here by the demonic sect.

00:25:12.740 --> 00:25:16.130 line:80%
Hundreds of years ago,
the world was in chaos.

00:25:17.370 --> 00:25:19.180 line:80%
We had fled here

00:25:19.180 --> 00:25:20.530 line:80%
to escape the war.

00:25:21.850 --> 00:25:22.646 line:80%
We thought

00:25:22.657 --> 00:25:23.631 line:80%
(Cai Anning)
the vines

00:25:23.655 --> 00:25:24.329 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:25:24.340 --> 00:25:25.540 line:80%
(Young Jiang)
were a shield.

00:25:25.564 --> 00:25:26.090 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:25:26.780 --> 00:25:28.180 line:80%
But the vine's essence

00:25:28.180 --> 00:25:30.420 line:80%
entered our blood

00:25:30.420 --> 00:25:31.780 line:80%
and was hereditary.

00:25:32.460 --> 00:25:34.460 line:80%
Not only were adults short-lived,

00:25:34.460 --> 00:25:36.700 line:80%
but children were weak and bent.

00:25:36.980 --> 00:25:38.530 line:80%
You have poison in your body.

00:25:39.130 --> 00:25:41.890 line:80%
After learning
about our village's plight,

00:25:42.610 --> 00:25:44.180 line:80%
the benefactor decided to stay

00:25:45.420 --> 00:25:47.220 line:80%
and use the seeds she brought

00:25:47.220 --> 00:25:49.330 line:80%
to develop a remedy.

00:25:49.330 --> 00:25:50.500 line:80%
What is this?

00:25:50.500 --> 00:25:51.500 line:80%
This is the Night Orchid.

00:25:52.090 --> 00:25:53.700 line:80%
We plant it together.

00:25:53.700 --> 00:25:56.370 line:80%
Perhaps it will cure your poison.

00:25:58.890 --> 00:26:00.500 line:80%
The Night Orchid indeed neutralized

00:26:00.500 --> 00:26:03.220 line:80%
the vine poison in our bodies.

00:26:04.610 --> 00:26:05.850 line:80%
Unfortunately,

00:26:06.890 --> 00:26:08.660 line:80%
the good times didn't last.

00:26:11.610 --> 00:26:13.180 line:80%
Rumors claimed our benefactor

00:26:13.180 --> 00:26:16.090 line:80%
had stolen the demonic sect's treasure

00:26:16.090 --> 00:26:17.760 line:80%
- and hid it here.
- Demoness!

00:26:17.780 --> 00:26:20.230 line:80%
- Many wanted to break in.
- Hand over

00:26:20.740 --> 00:26:21.780 line:80%
the treasure...

00:26:22.290 --> 00:26:23.420 line:80%
Hand it over...

00:26:23.700 --> 00:26:27.570 line:80%
They blamed all grievances on her.

00:26:31.180 --> 00:26:33.020 line:80%
She didn't defend herself

00:26:33.740 --> 00:26:36.700 line:80%
but instructed us to set up
the fog and maze,

00:26:36.700 --> 00:26:37.980 line:80%
sealed the Blood Marsh,

00:26:38.810 --> 00:26:42.290 line:80%
and spread fearsome rumors

00:26:42.570 --> 00:26:44.220 line:80%
to keep outsiders away.

00:26:48.130 --> 00:26:49.330 line:80%
Soon after,

00:26:49.780 --> 00:26:52.700 line:80%
our benefactor passed away.

00:26:57.290 --> 00:26:59.500 line:80%
If you hadn't come here,

00:27:00.050 --> 00:27:03.370 line:80%
you wouldn't have suffered such slander.

00:27:04.940 --> 00:27:06.370 line:80%
I don't regret it.

00:27:08.090 --> 00:27:10.500 line:80%
Saving so many people

00:27:12.050 --> 00:27:13.130 line:80%
was worth it.

00:27:38.940 --> 00:27:42.220 line:80%
Following her wishes,

00:27:42.220 --> 00:27:44.530 line:80%
we scattered her ashes.

00:27:44.530 --> 00:27:46.810 line:80%
Whenever we want to remember her,

00:27:46.810 --> 00:27:50.180 line:80%
we come and see these Night Orchids.

00:27:50.180 --> 00:27:52.090 line:80%
All of this was caused
by the greed of others.

00:27:53.740 --> 00:27:55.050 line:80%
Why blame her

00:27:55.610 --> 00:27:56.660 line:80%
and call her a demoness?

00:27:57.090 --> 00:27:58.460 line:80%
It's true.

00:27:58.460 --> 00:28:01.050 line:80%
It's a pity we can't leave the marsh

00:28:01.050 --> 00:28:03.850 line:80%
and clear her name.

00:28:09.370 --> 00:28:10.740 line:80%
Enough talking.

00:28:10.740 --> 00:28:13.020 line:80%
Your friends should be here.

00:28:13.020 --> 00:28:13.940 line:80%
I'll go check.

00:28:21.290 --> 00:28:22.740 line:80%
The Night Orchid here,

00:28:22.740 --> 00:28:24.180 line:80%
the Withered Branch of Qingque Sect,

00:28:24.180 --> 00:28:25.886 line:80%
and the Beichen Orchid
of Carefree Chamber

00:28:27.050 --> 00:28:29.130 line:80%
come from the same ancestral seed.

00:28:31.660 --> 00:28:33.500 line:80%
I wonder if Qingque Sect's
Withered Branch

00:28:34.130 --> 00:28:35.130 line:80%
has bloomed.

00:28:39.980 --> 00:28:40.820 line:80%
They have,

00:28:42.020 --> 00:28:43.610 line:80%
but my master used them to heal me.

00:28:49.610 --> 00:28:51.220 line:80%
My master has no interest in them.

00:28:51.980 --> 00:28:52.820 line:80%
But why are you

00:28:53.850 --> 00:28:55.570 line:80%
so concerned about the Night Orchid?

00:28:56.660 --> 00:28:57.740 line:80%
What is its true use?

00:29:00.420 --> 00:29:02.130 line:80%
Why did Mu Zhengyang want it?

00:29:07.980 --> 00:29:08.820 line:80%
What?

00:29:09.740 --> 00:29:11.700 line:80%
Zhao and Yuzhi were captured
by the demonic sect?

00:29:12.050 --> 00:29:13.703 line:80%
That day,
the Huangsha Gang lost control.

00:29:14.130 --> 00:29:16.290 line:80%
Zhao and Yuzhi left with Father.

00:29:16.290 --> 00:29:17.570 line:80%
Soon after, news came

00:29:17.940 --> 00:29:19.260 line:80%
that the demonic sect had arrived

00:29:19.500 --> 00:29:20.850 line:80%
and taken Zhao and others.

00:29:23.420 --> 00:29:24.740 line:80%
It must be Mu Qingyan again.

00:29:25.570 --> 00:29:26.410 line:80%
Father,

00:29:26.570 --> 00:29:27.663 line:80%
have you found any evidence

00:29:27.674 --> 00:29:29.940 line:80%
linking the corpse slaves
to the demonic sect?

00:29:33.570 --> 00:29:34.410 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:29:34.610 --> 00:29:35.610 line:80%
is my father alright?

00:29:36.290 --> 00:29:37.590 line:80%
Your father is in Luoying Valley.

00:29:37.890 --> 00:29:40.180 line:80%
Lord Cai is doing his best to treat him.

00:29:40.180 --> 00:29:42.220 line:80%
There is no threat to his life.

00:29:42.660 --> 00:29:43.500 line:80%
That's a relief.

00:29:44.180 --> 00:29:45.020 line:80%
That's a relief.

00:29:46.980 --> 00:29:48.420 line:80%
Thankfully, you're fine.

00:29:48.940 --> 00:29:50.420 line:80%
Yuzhi's life is safe too.

00:29:52.020 --> 00:29:52.860 line:80%
Zhao,

00:29:53.130 --> 00:29:54.980 line:80%
did Mu Qingyan give you a hard time?

00:29:55.500 --> 00:29:56.780 line:80%
Why would he trouble me?

00:29:58.180 --> 00:30:00.700 line:80%
Before, we stayed with them
because of Yuzhi.

00:30:00.700 --> 00:30:02.570 line:80%
Now that we've found the antidote,

00:30:02.570 --> 00:30:04.570 line:80%
let's leave once Yuzhi wakes up.

00:30:04.570 --> 00:30:06.980 line:80%
We mustn't get involved with them again.

00:30:06.980 --> 00:30:08.700 line:80%
What if Master finds out

00:30:08.700 --> 00:30:10.370 line:80%
and locks you up for another year?

00:30:13.330 --> 00:30:14.170 line:80%
We should leave.

00:30:16.180 --> 00:30:17.660 line:80%
But something still feels off to me.

00:30:22.570 --> 00:30:23.410 line:80%
Xingjia,

00:30:23.740 --> 00:30:24.740 line:80%
watch Yuzhi.

00:30:25.420 --> 00:30:26.370 line:80%
I'll go check outside.

00:30:37.700 --> 00:30:39.486 line:80%
You're indeed here
to take the Night Orchid.

00:30:39.780 --> 00:30:40.620 line:80%
Stop dreaming.

00:30:41.220 --> 00:30:42.740 line:80%
It's protected by a formation.

00:30:43.020 --> 00:30:44.295 line:80%
Only people from Luoying Valley

00:30:44.306 --> 00:30:45.130 line:80%
know how to break it.

00:30:52.890 --> 00:30:54.460 line:80%
The Night Orchid, like the saliva,

00:30:55.050 --> 00:30:57.130 line:80%
is a medium for cultivating
the Ziwei Method,

00:30:58.370 --> 00:30:59.210 line:80%
right?

00:31:06.530 --> 00:31:07.980 line:80%
From the saliva

00:31:09.530 --> 00:31:10.740 line:80%
to the Jade Sunflower

00:31:11.460 --> 00:31:12.780 line:80%
and now the Night Orchid,

00:31:14.020 --> 00:31:15.570 line:80%
it's all tied to the Ziwei Method.

00:31:16.810 --> 00:31:18.740 line:80%
Mu Zhengyang used the excuse
of helping a friend

00:31:19.130 --> 00:31:19.970 line:80%
to trick my aunt

00:31:20.290 --> 00:31:21.200 line:80%
into getting the saliva

00:31:21.211 --> 00:31:22.484 line:80%
and collecting the Night Orchid.

00:31:22.850 --> 00:31:24.940 line:80%
That's why my aunt was so upset

00:31:25.780 --> 00:31:27.130 line:80%
on her second visit.

00:31:29.700 --> 00:31:31.460 line:80%
She had learned the truth

00:31:32.330 --> 00:31:33.240 line:80%
and knew Mu Zhengyang

00:31:33.251 --> 00:31:35.040 line:80%
was using her to cultivate
the Ziwei Method.

00:31:35.810 --> 00:31:37.780 line:80%
But if Mu Zhengyang
has taken the Night Orchid,

00:31:38.740 --> 00:31:40.180 line:80%
why come a second time?

00:31:40.530 --> 00:31:42.103 line:80%
That's because the first time he took it

00:31:42.850 --> 00:31:44.850 line:80%
wasn't for his own cultivation.

00:31:46.420 --> 00:31:47.780 line:80%
It was offered to Nie Hengcheng.

00:31:50.050 --> 00:31:51.460 line:80%
I just realized this.

00:31:52.370 --> 00:31:53.890 line:80%
Mu Zhengyang told Xue Youfu

00:31:54.573 --> 00:31:56.120 line:80%
he wanted to reclaim the family estate,

00:31:56.220 --> 00:31:57.680 line:80%
but he couldn't defeat Nie Hengcheng.

00:31:58.370 --> 00:31:59.570 line:80%
So, there was only one way:

00:32:00.940 --> 00:32:02.660 line:80%
Use a peerless technique

00:32:03.810 --> 00:32:05.020 line:80%
to lure Nie Hengcheng.

00:32:07.050 --> 00:32:08.780 line:80%
Mu Zhengyang must've found
the Ziwei Method

00:32:08.780 --> 00:32:10.180 line:80%
at the Jiuzhou Archive

00:32:11.180 --> 00:32:13.500 line:80%
and used it to entice Nie Hengcheng
to practice it,

00:32:14.220 --> 00:32:15.780 line:80%
even deceiving my aunt to get

00:32:16.370 --> 00:32:17.980 line:80%
the Night Orchid and saliva.

00:32:20.420 --> 00:32:21.420 line:80%
But I can't understand

00:32:22.020 --> 00:32:23.370 line:80%
what method he used

00:32:23.940 --> 00:32:25.530 line:80%
to change Nie Hengcheng's temperament,

00:32:26.220 --> 00:32:27.740 line:80%
forcing all the Jianghu heroes

00:32:28.370 --> 00:32:29.890 line:80%
to unite against him.

00:32:31.050 --> 00:32:32.570 line:80%
As for the second trip,

00:32:33.370 --> 00:32:34.810 line:80%
that's because Mu Zhengyang

00:32:36.090 --> 00:32:38.420 line:80%
began practicing the Ziwei Method,

00:32:42.020 --> 00:32:43.290 line:80%
just like you.

00:32:47.570 --> 00:32:49.020 line:80%
Master was right.

00:32:50.570 --> 00:32:52.090 line:80%
All the men in the Mu clan

00:32:52.090 --> 00:32:53.090 line:80%
are skin-painted demons.

00:32:57.220 --> 00:32:58.700 line:80%
I'm not Mu Zhengyang.

00:33:00.420 --> 00:33:02.180 line:80%
I'll never become Nie Hengcheng.

00:33:02.780 --> 00:33:04.460 line:80%
I'll never let you take
the Night Orchid.

00:33:06.420 --> 00:33:07.530 line:80%
As I said,

00:33:08.420 --> 00:33:09.850 line:80%
if you insist,

00:33:11.020 --> 00:33:13.130 line:80%
I'll make you a ghost beneath my blade.

00:33:13.890 --> 00:33:14.730 line:80%
Zhao,

00:33:16.740 --> 00:33:17.940 line:80%
you can't stop me.

00:33:28.940 --> 00:33:30.500 line:80%
I heard that over the past year,

00:33:31.180 --> 00:33:33.020 line:80%
Song Yuzhi has been taking care of you.

00:33:33.370 --> 00:33:34.460 line:80%
None of your business.

00:33:35.020 --> 00:33:37.420 line:80%
Your blade is nothing special.

00:33:37.890 --> 00:33:39.130 line:80%
You haven't improved.

00:33:39.780 --> 00:33:40.620 line:80%
Take this.

00:33:58.180 --> 00:34:00.020 line:80%
You still can't forget old feelings.

00:34:00.700 --> 00:34:02.220 line:80%
I like that about you.

00:34:02.660 --> 00:34:03.740 line:80%
You can't forget me,

00:34:04.180 --> 00:34:05.850 line:80%
and you can't bear to kill me.

00:34:06.660 --> 00:34:07.660 line:80%
Madman.

00:34:07.970 --> 00:34:09.060 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:34:09.060 --> 00:34:10.330 line:80%
are you okay?

00:34:23.660 --> 00:34:24.580 line:80%
Zhao,

00:34:24.850 --> 00:34:26.290 line:80%
did you quarrel?

00:34:26.930 --> 00:34:28.660 line:80%
I've seen it all.

00:34:29.220 --> 00:34:30.740 line:80%
Pingshu also had quarrels

00:34:31.010 --> 00:34:33.450 line:80%
with Master Zhengyang,

00:34:33.780 --> 00:34:35.220 line:80%
just like you two.

00:34:36.490 --> 00:34:37.700 line:80%
They quarreled?

00:34:39.010 --> 00:34:39.850 line:80%
What was it about?

00:34:40.140 --> 00:34:41.700 line:80%
Young couples argue.

00:34:42.100 --> 00:34:43.395 line:80%
It's always about who likes whom

00:34:43.406 --> 00:34:46.540 line:80%
and who doesn't.

00:34:47.220 --> 00:34:48.180 line:80%
But he was willing

00:34:48.540 --> 00:34:50.100 line:80%
to risk his life for you,

00:34:50.100 --> 00:34:52.850 line:80%
breaking through the fog and maze.

00:34:53.580 --> 00:34:55.810 line:80%
That shows you mean more

00:34:55.810 --> 00:34:57.620 line:80%
to him than himself.

00:35:03.060 --> 00:35:03.900 line:80%
It's you again.

00:35:05.140 --> 00:35:06.780 line:80%
Do you have anything to do

00:35:06.780 --> 00:35:08.010 line:80%
with the corpse slaves?

00:35:08.010 --> 00:35:08.850 line:80%
Hold it.

00:35:09.180 --> 00:35:10.580 line:80%
Stop making baseless accusations.

00:35:10.580 --> 00:35:12.060 line:80%
It was your family who did it.

00:35:12.060 --> 00:35:13.660 line:80%
Why blame us?

00:35:13.660 --> 00:35:14.970 line:80%
My father was framed.

00:35:15.970 --> 00:35:16.810 line:80%
Mr. Song,

00:35:17.060 --> 00:35:18.620 line:80%
didn't Fan tell you

00:35:18.810 --> 00:35:19.890 line:80%
how you were poisoned?

00:35:21.620 --> 00:35:22.460 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:35:22.700 --> 00:35:24.006 line:80%
we didn't have time to tell you.

00:35:24.660 --> 00:35:26.490 line:80%
The poisoned weapon that hit you

00:35:26.709 --> 00:35:28.792 line:80%
was likely used by someone
familiar with your skills

00:35:28.850 --> 00:35:30.450 line:80%
and someone you didn't suspect.

00:35:31.290 --> 00:35:32.890 line:80%
From the circumstances,

00:35:34.290 --> 00:35:35.620 line:80%
it was most likely...

00:35:35.970 --> 00:35:36.890 line:80%
Who?

00:35:36.890 --> 00:35:37.750 line:80%
Tell me.

00:35:37.770 --> 00:35:38.740 line:80%
Xiuzhi.

00:35:39.540 --> 00:35:40.380 line:80%
My brother?

00:35:43.930 --> 00:35:44.890 line:80%
It can't be him.

00:35:45.660 --> 00:35:46.890 line:80%
He's not that kind of man.

00:35:48.700 --> 00:35:50.620 line:80%
He's always gentle and peaceful,

00:35:50.620 --> 00:35:51.460 line:80%
never aggressive.

00:35:52.370 --> 00:35:53.700 line:80%
How could he do such a thing?

00:35:54.450 --> 00:35:55.890 line:80%
Is it hard to understand?

00:35:55.890 --> 00:35:58.410 line:80%
Everyone knows Lord Song favors you.

00:35:58.410 --> 00:36:00.450 line:80%
You are Qi Yunke's disciple

00:36:00.450 --> 00:36:02.330 line:80%
and Yin Qinglian's son,

00:36:02.330 --> 00:36:04.100 line:80%
grandson of Yin Dai.

00:36:04.100 --> 00:36:05.810 line:80%
In the future, Guangtian Sect

00:36:05.810 --> 00:36:07.890 line:80%
and Qingque Sect will be yours.

00:36:07.890 --> 00:36:09.370 line:80%
Now, look at your brother.

00:36:09.370 --> 00:36:12.180 line:80%
His skills are inferior to yours;
his status is lower.

00:36:12.180 --> 00:36:14.700 line:80%
He doesn't even know who his mother is.

00:36:14.700 --> 00:36:16.100 line:80%
If he didn't remove you,

00:36:16.100 --> 00:36:18.290 line:80%
when would he ever get ahead?

00:36:18.290 --> 00:36:19.450 line:80%
Mr. Song,

00:36:19.450 --> 00:36:20.740 line:80%
as I've told you before,

00:36:20.740 --> 00:36:23.290 line:80%
the Six Sects are no good either.

00:36:23.290 --> 00:36:24.540 line:80%
That day outside,

00:36:24.540 --> 00:36:26.780 line:80%
Siqi Sect even used
the Curved Formation.

00:36:26.780 --> 00:36:29.580 line:80%
Yang Heying is likely in cahoots
with your brother.

00:36:30.370 --> 00:36:31.290 line:80%
By the way,

00:36:31.290 --> 00:36:32.450 line:80%
I heard

00:36:32.450 --> 00:36:33.970 line:80%
Yang Heying's daughter

00:36:34.580 --> 00:36:35.850 line:80%
is marrying your brother.

00:36:37.540 --> 00:36:40.970 line:80%
Truly, a loving family.

00:36:41.810 --> 00:36:42.650 line:80%
Are you thirsty?

00:36:42.930 --> 00:36:43.780 line:80%
Drink some water.

00:36:44.740 --> 00:36:45.580 line:80%
Wait.

00:36:46.370 --> 00:36:47.810 line:80%
I'll investigate

00:36:47.810 --> 00:36:49.140 line:80%
the truth.

00:36:49.140 --> 00:36:51.540 line:80%
The corpse slaves may have
nothing to do with you,

00:36:51.540 --> 00:36:53.780 line:80%
but your appearing nearby

00:36:53.780 --> 00:36:54.930 line:80%
is too much of a coincidence.

00:36:56.620 --> 00:36:58.180 line:80%
What are your intentions?

00:36:58.459 --> 00:37:00.299 line:80%
Our trip has nothing to do
with the Six Sects.

00:37:01.220 --> 00:37:02.060 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:37:03.930 --> 00:37:04.970 line:80%
long time no see.

00:37:05.580 --> 00:37:07.410 line:80%
Last time, it was the pity ploy.

00:37:08.540 --> 00:37:10.810 line:80%
I wonder
what strategy you have this time.

00:37:12.700 --> 00:37:14.700 line:80%
You've become fond of joking.

00:37:15.180 --> 00:37:16.580 line:80%
Have you read too many novels?

00:37:18.850 --> 00:37:19.690 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:37:20.410 --> 00:37:21.250 line:80%
do me a favor.

00:37:25.410 --> 00:37:26.250 line:80%
I'll go too.

00:37:31.410 --> 00:37:32.850 line:80%
We should leave here asap.

00:37:32.850 --> 00:37:34.220 line:80%
It's pounding

00:37:34.220 --> 00:37:35.140 line:80%
in my little chest.

00:37:35.396 --> 00:37:36.876 line:80%
Tonight, we return to Guangtian Sect.

00:37:37.180 --> 00:37:38.490 line:80%
I must ask Xiuzhi for the truth.

00:37:38.890 --> 00:37:40.290 line:80%
I wonder how Father is doing.

00:37:40.740 --> 00:37:42.450 line:80%
Lord Song looks with longevity.

00:37:42.780 --> 00:37:43.780 line:80%
He'll be fine.

00:37:44.100 --> 00:37:45.490 line:80%
As for your brother,

00:37:46.850 --> 00:37:48.540 line:80%
it has happened.

00:37:48.540 --> 00:37:49.660 line:80%
Better accept it.

00:37:49.660 --> 00:37:51.290 line:80%
At least we've seen his true face.

00:37:54.100 --> 00:37:54.970 line:80%
I was wrong too.

00:37:54.970 --> 00:37:56.620 line:80%
Knowing he's belittled by the sect

00:37:56.620 --> 00:37:57.890 line:80%
due to his birth,

00:37:58.490 --> 00:37:59.890 line:80%
I didn't step in to help.

00:38:01.660 --> 00:38:02.850 line:80%
Even so,

00:38:02.850 --> 00:38:05.010 line:80%
he shouldn't commit such atrocities

00:38:05.010 --> 00:38:06.010 line:80%
and harm others.

00:38:07.140 --> 00:38:07.980 line:80%
If he

00:38:08.580 --> 00:38:10.490 line:80%
really colluded with Yang Heying

00:38:10.490 --> 00:38:12.370 line:80%
to kill the Huangsha Gang and innocents,

00:38:13.180 --> 00:38:14.100 line:80%
I'll never let him off.

00:38:16.180 --> 00:38:17.410 line:80%
You're sensible.

00:38:19.450 --> 00:38:21.580 line:80%
Master should be at Guangtian Sect.

00:38:21.580 --> 00:38:22.450 line:80%
Then,

00:38:22.450 --> 00:38:23.540 line:80%
right and wrong

00:38:23.540 --> 00:38:24.850 line:80%
will be decided.

00:38:25.410 --> 00:38:26.780 line:80%
Before that,

00:38:26.780 --> 00:38:28.850 line:80%
I want Xingjia to do me a favor.

00:38:28.850 --> 00:38:29.690 line:80%
A favor?

00:38:37.480 --> 00:38:48.140 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:39:06.900 --> 00:39:11.310 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:39:11.875 --> 00:39:16.490 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:39:16.830 --> 00:39:21.395 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:39:21.920 --> 00:39:26.220 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:39:29.165 --> 00:39:33.865 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:34.390 --> 00:39:38.680 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:39:39.340 --> 00:39:43.370 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:39:43.685 --> 00:39:48.810 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:39:49.385 --> 00:39:54.195 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:54.410 --> 00:39:58.580 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:39:59.305 --> 00:40:03.240 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:40:03.740 --> 00:40:09.015 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:40:31.745 --> 00:40:36.875 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:40:37.240 --> 00:40:41.610 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:40:41.875 --> 00:40:46.005 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:40:46.190 --> 00:40:51.765 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪